dmca.title: slander/defamation/libel
dmca.body:
During a Bell South Search it has come to my attention that SWCreations.net is implying that MiShelliDesigns.com has violated copyright and has be prosecuted.  This implication can be found on http://www.SWCreations.net/copyright.html

Due to the fact that SWCreations.net has the #1 position in google search and receives millions of web page hits each month, we feel this notice has unfairly hampered the growth of our company do to the inability to seek out quality links to increase our search engine ratings.  In our opinion this is abuse and needs to be removed immediately.
